{
  "texts": [
    "This is because TM provides an automated and efficient approach for uncovering hidden and coherent themes in the research documents.",
    "TM helps identify prevalent research areas and emerging trends which aid in unveiling the current and future research pathways of the subject.",
    "For example, Alhashmi et al. (2023) extracted documents from Scopus to present an overview of AI's current healthcare research landscape by adopting LDA to identify both explicit and implicit topics from 2334 documents.",
    "Despite the huge benefits of TM, the knowledge of study on TM development is limited, especially from the perspective of bibliometrics analysis, and remains fully untapped.",
    "Prior studies like Li and Lei (2021) performed a bibliometric analysis of TM studies from 2000 to 2017 using 1171 articles."
  ]
}